{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-bracket-notation-to-find-the-nth-character-in-a-string","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Koristite Uglastu Notaciju za N-ti Karakter u Stringu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Takodje mozete koristiti <dfn>uglaste zagrade</dfn> da pristupite karakteru na odredjenoj poziciji u stringu.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da racunari brojanje pocinju od <code>0</code>, pa je prvi karakter zapravo na poziciji nula.</p>\n<p>Primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const firstName = \"Ada\";\nconst secondLetterOfFirstName = firstName[1];\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>secondLetterOfFirstName</code> ce imati vrednost stringa <code>d</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bd7123c9c450eddfaeb5bdef","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavite <code>thirdLetterOfLastName</code> tako da bude jednako trecem karakteru promenljive <code>lastName</code> koristeci uglastu notaciju.</p>\n<p><strong>Savet:</strong> Pogledajte primer iznad ako zapnete.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18343,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-bracket-notation-to-find-the-nth-character-in-a-string"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nconst lastName = \"Lovelace\";\n\n// Only change code below this line\nconst thirdLetterOfLastName = lastName; // Change this line","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Promenljiva <code>thirdLetterOfLastName</code> treba da ima vrednost <code>v</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(thirdLetterOfLastName === 'v');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite uglastu notaciju.</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/thirdLetterOfLastName\\s*=\\s*lastName\\s*\\[\\s*\\d\\s*\\]/));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"use-bracket-notation-to-find-the-nth-character-in-a-string","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-bracket-notation-to-find-the-last-character-in-a-string","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understand-string-immutability","id":"bd7123c9c450eddfaeb5bdef","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-bracket-notation-to-find-the-nth-character-in-a-string"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}